<h3 class="govuk-heading-m">Find your login credentials</h3>

<ol class="govuk-list govuk-list--number govuk-list--spaced">
  <li>
    <strong>Open the CloudFormation console</strong> in your sandbox account and find the <code>ndx-try-localgov-ims</code> stack.
  </li>
  <li>
    <strong>Go to the Outputs tab</strong> — you'll find:
    <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
      <li><strong>AdminPortalUrl</strong> — the HTTPS URL for the admin interface</li>
      <li><strong>PaymentPortalUrl</strong> — the HTTPS URL for the citizen payment portal</li>
      <li><strong>AdminUsername</strong> — <code>admin</code> (but you'll log in with the email below)</li>
      <li><strong>AdminPassword</strong> — the generated password for all users</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>
    <strong>Open the Admin Portal URL</strong> in your browser. You'll see the login page.
  </li>
  <li>
    <strong>Log in</strong> with:
    <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
      <li><strong>Email:</strong> <code>tester1@your-organisation.com</code></li>
      <li><strong>Password:</strong> the AdminPassword from CloudFormation outputs</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ol>

<div class="govuk-inset-text">
  <strong>Tip:</strong> The system has several pre-configured users with different roles. You can also log in as <code>tester2@your-organisation.com</code> with the same password.
</div>
